  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study addresses the influence of anesthesia induction, ventilation and influence of
      cardiac surgical procedures and cardio-pulmonary-bypass on right ventricular function.
      Influence on patient outcome is also studied. Three dimensional echocardiography is applied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
